00:03:28.050 --> 00:03:30.590 align:middle line:90%
and examples.

00:03:30.590 --> 00:03:33.080 align:middle line:84%
I was meeting a
friend for lunch,

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:36.170 align:middle line:84%
and this friend was
