00:03:59.870 --> 00:04:05.240 align:middle line:84%
but instead, this
individual said, June 8?

00:04:05.240 --> 00:04:06.110 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:04:06.110 --> 00:04:08.480 align:middle line:84%
That is my incest
support group meeting

00:04:08.480 --> 00:04:10.160 align:middle line:84%
and I never let
these people down.

00:04:10.160 --> 00:04:13.140 align:middle line:84%
I'm always there on June 8,
