00:04:19.610 --> 00:04:20.450 align:middle line:90%
minutes.

00:04:20.450 --> 00:04:24.470 align:middle line:84%
Now this individual who had
asked the question said,

00:04:24.470 --> 00:04:26.870 align:middle line:90%
oh, OK, and walked away.

00:04:26.870 --> 00:04:32.900 align:middle line:84%
But I watched a
unbelievable display

00:04:32.900 --> 00:04:38.720 align:middle line:84%
of information roll out of her
