00:04:55.160 --> 00:04:59.090 align:middle line:84%
that her intention in
communicating that information

00:04:59.090 --> 00:05:02.090 align:middle line:90%
was that she wanted them--

00:05:02.090 --> 00:05:06.320 align:middle line:84%
everybody at the table to
treat her in a certain way

00:05:06.320 --> 00:05:11.690 align:middle line:84%
because she was a, quote-quote,
"victim" of incest.

00:05:11.690 --> 00:05:14.300 align:middle line:90%
She had an agenda.

00:05:14.300 --> 00:05:17.880 align:middle line:84%
Later, when we were sitting
at lunch, I said to her,

00:05:17.880 --> 00:05:19.380 align:middle line:90%
I have to ask you a question--

00:05:19.380 --> 00:05:22.340 align:middle line:84%
